# Magento Cypress Test Automation
This project contains Cypress automated tests for a Magento e-commerce application.

## ðŸ“¦ Prerequisites

- Node.js >= 16
- npm or yarn

## ðŸš€ Getting Started

### Clone the repo

```bash
git clone https://github.com/attuye/magento-cypress-tests.git
cd magneto-automation

```
### Install dependencies
npm install

### Add .env file
Create a .env file in the root directory with the following variables:

USER_EMAIL=your-test-user
USER_PASSWORD=your-test-password

### Running Tests
Headed(with browser)
```bash
npx cypress open
```
Headless and Generate HTML Report
```bash
npx cypress run
```
The generated HTML report will be found under cypress/reports folder, i.e mochawesome.html
Sample report is already added.
